{"TopicId":210826,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Sports","CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-27T04:15:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kerbalsaurus","CreatedById":222386,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-27T04:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if on EVA, Kerbals can play little sports games? I know this is a dumb thing to suggest, but I feel it\u2019d be a nice little thing to do to have fun with your Kerbals. Think \u00A0about it. Launching a golf ball into orbit on Gilly, low-gravity catch on the Mun, and Jebediah absolutely shredding those waves on Laythe. It\u2019s definitely more of a novelty feature, but it\u2019d give you more to do on EVA than science and flags.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoldForest","CreatedById":77770,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-27T09:17:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually think this is a neat idea worth implementing. Maybe not as say a full on you can actually play golf or throw a football or etcetera, but more animations of the Kerbals doing stuff would be nice, yeah.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tajwo","CreatedById":222600,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-27T09:30:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/DaHM8DmC84I?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Celebrate the Kerbin Cup!\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"emord-nillap","CreatedById":223976,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-27T16:33:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike the Eva science kits, but better\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-11-28T11:32:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeifra